├═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════┤
║                                                                   ║
║  6a. Build full MSA                                               ║
║      ├── Sample + top 50 BLAST hits + all curated outbreak refs   ║
║      ├── MAFFT (auto strategy or L-INS-i for accuracy)            ║
